</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep id="30BF2E30FF8AEE6EFF16FCC0F49228CB" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">
<paragraph id="8BF43695FF8AEE6EFF16FCC0F49328AB" blockId="24.[192,1441,456,1339]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">
<keyLead id="30BA95A0FF8AEE6EFF16FCC0F49328AB" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">
3(1). Basal margin of pronotum with a belt of coarse contiguous punctures crenulating a sort of thick edge (
<figureCitation id="13702A10FF8AEE6EFEBAFCA0F0E7284B" box="[364,468,840,859]" captionStart="Figure 109-119" captionStartId="41.[192,279,1783,1800]" captionTargetBox="[306,1315,216,1712]" captionTargetId="figure-87@41.[264,1368,192,1754]" captionTargetPageId="41" captionText="Figure 109-119. Gonaphodiopsis hypogea, new species (Salamander Cave, Rancho del Cielo, Gomes Farias, Tamaulipas, Mexico). 109) Epipharynx. 110-111) Habitus (length ideogram and morphological details). 112- 113) Aedeagus (dorsal and lateral view). Gonaphodiopsis montesdeocai, new species (Xuatusco env., Parada de los Pinos, Veracruz, Mexico). 114) Epipharynx. 115-116) Habitus (morphological details and length ideogram). 117) Right labial palp (dorsal view). 118-119) Aedeagus (dorsal and lateral view)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5174242" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5174242/files/figure.png" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Fig. 111</figureCitation>
); lateral margins of pronotum slightly inwardly sinuate before hind angles; truncation of hind angle inwardly sinuate; elytral interstriae slightly convex on disc, subcariniform on preapical declivity. Chestnut brown more or less dark. Length 5.0-5.5 mm. 
<collectingCountry id="F35C7605FF8AEE6EFEF6FC40F04A28AB" box="[288,377,936,955]" name="Mexico" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Mexico</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingRegion id="498FF877FF8AEE6EFE5EFC40F36328AB" box="[392,592,936,955]" country="Mexico" name="San Luis Potosi" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">San Luis Potosí</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="498FF877FF8AEE6EFD8AFC40F3C628AB" box="[604,757,936,955]" country="Mexico" name="Tamaulipas" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Tamaulipas</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="498FF877FF8AEE6EFCD6FC40F24128AB" box="[768,882,936,955]" country="Mexico" name="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Veracruz</collectingRegion>
) ............................ 
